flowchart TD
    A["CostHamiltonian H_C"] --> B["augmented_ising_graph()<br/>weight matrix W"]
    B --> C["SDP relaxation (solved once)<br/>max &Sigma; W_ij (1 - X_ij)/2, diag(X) = 1, X &#8829; 0"]
    C --> D["Factor X = V V^T<br/>via eigendecomposition"]
    D --> E["Repeat n_shots times"]
    E --> F["Random hyperplane r (seeded)<br/>signs = sign(V &middot; r)"]
    F --> G["Partition -> bits_from_partition()"]
    G --> H["energy(x) = &langle;H_C&rangle;"]
    H --> I{"more roundings?"}
    I -->|yes| E
    I -->|no| J["n_shots sampled energies<br/>(best is GW value)"]
